            %strong What can the factoring proceeds be used for?
          %p There are no limitations to the use of funds. Your business can use the working capital that your factor provides to pay for ongoing expenses such as rent, utilities, vehicle repair, tolls, fuel, materials to fulfill orders, employee payroll, miscellaneous vendor bills, etc.
