            %strong Is receivable factoring the same as receivable financing?
          %p No.
          %p Receivable financing (a.k.a. invoice financing) is an asset-based loan that uses your invoices as collateral.
          %p Receivable factoring is not a loan.  It does not add debt to your ledgers and does not require monthly payments to the factor from your part.
